Class mxGraphBridge

java.lang.Object
  org.jgraph.graph.mxGraphBridge

public class mxGraphBridge
extends Object

Utility class to convert JGraph 5 data structures to JGraph 6 (X). Currently it is only designed to bridge the JGraph 5 layout facade
